{"tid":1538563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一國非兩制 港非港 你仲信個政府嗎?","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:21:05.000Z","uid":229436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5f2c9252401f888cbd986ad0fb05acf39e6e11","tid":1538563,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"5大訴求係一開始的事<br />\n依家已經認清依個政府係敵示香港人<br />\n就算佢話撤回都肯定唔會話係回應示 威者<br />\n佢只會話要一直去清算d暴徒 咁為我地付出未來的手足就會白白欺生左<br />\n林奠會話撤回係聽&quot;社會&quot;的&quot;聲音&quot;<br />\n一定唔會提示威者 唔會提係因為好多人出黎抗議<br />\n示威者=/=社會的聲音<br />\n政府已經將反對聲音=小強=暴力<br />\n如果我地香港人唔依一刻開始切底地反抗政府<br />\n日後只會有第二條送終法出現<br />\n<br />\n送終法係依個政府 依個由中共控制的政府諗出黎<br />\n中共不斷利用依個政府去洗盡我地香港人的錢 洗盡我地香港人的未來<br />\n仲有建制派 仲有警隊 依2個癌症 唔會係保留依個政府就解決到<br />\n因為佢地係互相依付 <br />\n要清走警隊=一定要先清理個政府<br />\n要清走建制=一定要先清理個政府<br />\n要清個政府=一定要將中共的魔爪拔走<br />\n<br />\n如果唔咁做我地未來 我地下一代一定只會不斷loop係同一個局入面!<br />\n而佢地會不斷係依幾十年內 推行更多反人道的條例去限制我地未來發聲抗爭的自由<br />\n會不斷助大警隊的權力 去防止我地未來再一次面對不公的時候企出黎反抗佢地<br />\n<br />\n所以5大訴求係咪滿足曬就得? 你仲信個政府嗎? 我地依家係要不斷尋求方法同出路<br />\n去令我地未來香港/自身未來有個安全自己民主的生活<br />\n<br />\n活係依個政府下 你有機會達成民主自由嗎??<br />\n如果無咁我地應該做d咩?<br />\n我地真係得番一條路可以行 我地絕對唔係政府的同路人 我地條路要由自己行番出黎"},{"pid":"68b1ed104e9c18e7bd8896f0da71b5134379dc98","tid":1538563,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81b1adf60cb34df57f6ac1f0d723abef765136a9","tid":1538563,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0898b7c2c1cab1cb64607a316bd75ee021486193","tid":1538563,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bad50b57ab892a8608a4362fe921dbd53be372","tid":1538563,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8bf5df71dd0dc80aede31a828a682af8ea0b7e","tid":1538563,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ecf4546a4b900898460f4fdc4a6895f0998b9a","tid":1538563,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd8b8f4021a08df7f52d11ce4cb4618c9c89b9e","tid":1538563,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c351d148959c7f0b8c8c01b5d6b673db68d443","tid":1538563,"uid":278434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思, 借Po<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1539894/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1539894/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"efdd5deab76221cfdfc67e5dd2d0fc1d53072bfe","tid":1538563,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />臭西"}]}